{"tid":1001293,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★銀聯雲閃付贊助維園年宵快餐檔　無得用八達通付款","createTime":"2019-01-30T04:43:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-30T14:24:25.000Z","uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":106,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"6dca3ff76ea13fc7c5db8bca81ac31aa09b9e278","tid":1001293,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T04:43:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2383472/org/99e3df65ab7071434c198f75db2f953d.jpg/iGN9pn_7aV54PKZFnkbXJYhSL9jWKUxT1yWEXNclhFw?v=w1440r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2383472%2Forg%2F99e3df65ab7071434c198f75db2f953d.jpg%2FiGN9pn_7aV54PKZFnkbXJYhSL9jWKUxT1yWEXNclhFw%3Fv%3Dw1440r16_9&h=f6793070&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一連七日的年宵市場將於今日（30日）起舉行，相信會吸引到不少市民到場「行大運」。其中全港最大的維園年宵市場，場內熟食檔向來人山人海。記者今日發現，三個快餐檔均獲銀聯「雲閃付」贊助，檔位掛滿宣傳牌。<br />\n<br />\n其中一檔負責人王先生説，會出售日式小食，強調「好有創意」，又希望可以為香港「製造繁榮」。不過要留意，小食檔不接受八達通付款，只接受現金或雲閃付；如想獲得優惠，便需使用「雲閃付」付款。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/289273/%E8%B1%AC%E5%B9%B42019-%E9%8A%80%E8%81%AF%E9%9B%B2%E9%96%83%E4%BB%98%E8%B4%8A%E5%8A%A9%E7%B6%AD%E5%9C%92%E5%B9%B4%E5%AE%B5%E5%BF%AB%E9%A4%90%E6%AA%94-%E7%84%A1%E5%BE%97%E7%94%A8%E5%85%AB%E9%81%94%E9%80%9A%E4%BB%98%E6%AC%BE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F289273%2F%25E8%25B1%25AC%25E5%25B9%25B42019-%25E9%258A%2580%25E8%2581%25AF%25E9%259B%25B2%25E9%2596%2583%25E4%25BB%2598%25E8%25B4%258A%25E5%258A%25A9%25E7%25B6%25AD%25E5%259C%2592%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E5%25AE%25B5%25E5%25BF%25AB%25E9%25A4%2590%25E6%25AA%2594-%25E7%2584%25A1%25E5%25BE%2597%25E7%2594%25A8%25E5%2585%25AB%25E9%2581%2594%25E9%2580%259A%25E4%25BB%2598%25E6%25AC%25BE&d=CddLi1wVc%2F0RDzQLDYdfB6nyrFheAedOz%2Bkyyi3ikZI%3D&h=5b8fdc3c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/289273/%E8%B1%AC%E5%B9